HEADWORD: Inelaborate
<hw>In`e*lab"o*rate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>inelaboratus</ets>. See <er>In-</er> not, and
<er>Elaborate</er>.]</ety> <def>Not elaborate; not wrought with care;
